Or will this level go like every other level in this series so far?  Thanks to Catobyte for the early access to the 1.0 update of the game!

attributes.title: Cursed Halo Forces us to MATH?
attributes.caption: I hope you brought your library card because today on Cursed Halo we are playing through 343 Guilty Spark and The Library.  The Flood finally enter the scene forcing Michael and Gavin to use hoglets, pee guns, and minecraft potions to navigate the dark swamp and multi-tiered library hall.

attributes.title: The END of Cursed Halo Again
attributes.caption: It's cursed, it's Halo, and it's broken.  The end of Cursed Halo again has arrived... AGAIN.  In their final act, Michael and Gavin venture through the finally playable and slightly broken "Keyes" and make an epic escape off the Halo ring in "The Maw".

attributes.title: The Final Level - Super Bunny Man (#22)
attributes.caption: This is it. Level 50. They said it couldn't be done. They said, the Summer Bois? They'll never see the end of Hopstacle Stadium. Well, who's laughing now?!
